675
00:40:38,540 --> 00:40:39,739
I said I'm not hungry.

676
00:40:40,020 --> 00:40:41,460
Take it away.

677
00:40:44,219 --> 00:40:44,739
Sir,

678
00:40:45,379 --> 00:40:47,259
then I'll leave the tray outside.

679
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:49,299
You can take it in when you want to eat.

